.wholesale.description:
All of the Antonini products are available at wholesale with minimum purchases to the retailer for sale in their shop.  

Additionally, there are many options available for most of the products with a minimum purchase, such as carbon or stainless blade, handle color or material, or type of knife edge.  Promotional customizing, such as imprinting a logo or text on handle or blade are also available for many Antonini products.

Please feel free to contact us at GSI Distributing for any wholesale for resale needs or questions you may have.
